.TH "LIGHTNING-INVOICE-QR" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-invoice-qr \- render a BOLT11 invoice as a QR code
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning invoice-qr
.I bolt11
.SH DESCRIPTION
Renders the given BOLT11 invoice as a UTF-8 QR code using qrencode.
.PP
Output: JSON object with bolt11 and qr (UTF-8 text) fields.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-invoice-decode (1)
